<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火花在狼周围飞舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们吓得后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要离开森林！”毛克利喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要住在村庄里。人类会对我很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走向一堆树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我必须还债。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓起一根树枝，在火里点着了它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他朝谢尔坎走去，拿着树枝贴近了老虎的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记住这个，谢尔坎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利厉声说：“下次我来到岩石会议时，我会带着你的皮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥着燃烧的树枝靠近老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，阿克拉自由了，你杀不了他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>树枝上的火猛烈地燃烧着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利左右挥舞着树枝，把老虎吓跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大部分狼也跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当火花落在皮毛上时，他们发出阵阵嚎叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉和巴希拉急忙走向毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利难过得大口喘气，脸上流着泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我怎么了，巴希拉？”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么我感觉这么奇怪？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你很难过，所以你在哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有人类才会像你一样流泪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利坐下，哭了一阵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，他站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在要回到洞里去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早上，我会跟狼妈妈和狼爸爸说再见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，年轻的狼们痛苦地嚎叫着，毛克利站在洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不会忘了我的，是吧？”毛克利问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对不会！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只叫格瑞布拉德的狼保证道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“偶尔在山底下见我们吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们可以在那里跟你玩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会想你的，毛克利。”狼妈妈温柔地说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就会见你们的。”毛克利保证道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他离开了洞，独自一人走下了山坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利沿着山谷的凹凸不平的小路走了几个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，这条路的尽头出现一片广阔的平原。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>平原上有很多大石头和大树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>成群的牛和水牛在平原上吃草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在远处，毛克利看见了一个村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个孩子在放牧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们看见毛克利时，吓得大叫着跑开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利饿了，他朝村庄走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他走到大门时，一个男人走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利张开嘴，指着嘴里表示他饿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人惊讶地看着毛克利，然后转身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他高喊着 “村长”跑掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，一个穿着白色衣服的胖男人来到了门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的额头上有一个彩色的印记。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身后是一大群人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都盯着毛克利看，对着毛克利指指点点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类没有礼貌。”毛克利想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有猴子才会这么做！”他朝人群皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没什么好怕的。” 村长对人群说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看这孩子胳膊和腿上的这些痕迹，都是狼咬的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可能是从森林里逃出来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的孩子！”几个女人说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是一个帅男孩儿。”一个女人说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个女人倒吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦苏雅 ！他看起来像你的儿子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>被老虎偷走的那个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个手腕和脚踝上戴着铜环的女人走上前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她仔细看着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不确定他是不是我的孩子。”她最后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他看起来确实像我儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村长举起双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林带走了什么，又还回来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把孩子带回家吧，麦苏雅。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>